cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SE, cs.DC 

This paper discusses the challenges of evaluating machine learning and deep learning models, which are common topics in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also proposes a solution for addressing these challenges, which involves specifying and provisioning experiments, which could fall under the sub-categories of cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
